{Speech 6}{}{[You see a big, burly man. He's doesn't look very friendly] This is a robbery, buddy. Passing through will cost you 100 coins - or broken bones. Do you like broken bones? Ha-ha-ha.@@[Suddenly, a brutish man with a sinister glint in his eye appears. You get a bad feeling about this] Well, well, well. What do we have here? Hand over your money. 100 coins and I'll let you go.}
